{"2897180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "反叛！吉蘇魯村的起義！", "steam_appid": 2897180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897180/extras/6150876646c833da67e14991220dcf6a.webp?t=1762767049\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉蘇魯村。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是個被豐富大自然包圍的山村。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村莊裡居民感情融洽，農業興盛，每個人都過著幸福的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是自從國家施行了蠻橫的政策，村民們的生活便變得困難起來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受村民們關照的旅人「瓦格納斯」見狀，毅然決然決定發起革命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而這個國家的士兵全都是「女性」………<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897180/extras/ad1f874c7b4f10994350517ba5625799.webp?t=1762767049\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一個關卡式的RPG動作遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通過擊敗每個關卡中的女性士兵並俘虜她們，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就可以觀看色情事件，並推動故事的發展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以把抓到的士兵賣去當妓女獲取大量金錢，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以把她們丟進自行開設的牧場回收道具，進一步解鎖色情事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897180/extras/7437fccfe0e651a57594ac949908b15d.webp?t=1762767049\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過用劍攻擊女兵，便可以打倒她們。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若是接觸到敵人就會受到傷害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當主角的HP歸零時，就會進入被敵人侮辱的敗北畫面中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（為了能夠輕易觸發敗北，在各種地方都配有毒沼，可以多加利用。）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\